task.summary: Added default response if response-variable query returns nothing.
Added data ingestion to cs minor.

Updated parse_questions to include team names.
Also updated createTables.sql to add the column.

Added example test to variable_normalizer.
Currently the test fails

Added periodic scraping.
Running the discord bot will now rerun the scraper once per day.
Added --scrape CLI option to main.
Running python main.py --scrape will now immediately trigger the scraper then exit.

Added query tests.
Added --test and --test-verbose flag to main to run the query tests.

Added --init flag to main.
Running this flag will empty the database, recreate all tables, ingest the questions form questions.txt, and run all scrapers.

Removed circular dependency.
Several scrapers had an unused import to data sustainer.
Fixed a bug in cli chat interface.
